---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="django-main-container">
    <section class="django-header">
      <svg class="django-icon" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="color:#092e20"><title>Django</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M11.146 0h3.924v18.166c-2.013.382-3.491.535-5.096.535-4.791 0-7.288-2.166-7.288-6.32 0-4.002 2.65-6.6 6.753-6.6.637 0 1.121.05 1.707.203zm0 9.143a3.894 3.894 0 00-1.325-.204c-1.988 0-3.134 1.223-3.134 3.365 0 2.09 1.096 3.236 3.109 3.236.433 0 .79-.025 1.35-.102V9.142zM21.314 6.06v9.098c0 3.134-.229 4.638-.917 5.937-.637 1.249-1.478 2.039-3.211 2.905l-3.644-1.733c1.733-.815 2.574-1.53 3.109-2.625.561-1.121.739-2.421.739-5.835V6.059h3.924zM17.39.021h3.924v4.026H17.39z"/></svg>
      <h1>Django</h1>
      <p>(Framework web para Python)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="django-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Introducción y arquitectura de Django</li>
        <li>Modelos, vistas y templates</li>
        <li>Buenas prácticas y ejemplos</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="django-quote">"Django hace que el desarrollo web en Python sea rápido y seguro."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.django-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.django-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.django-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #092e20;
}
.django-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #092e20;
}
.django-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.django-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #092e20;
}
.django-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.django-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.django-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #e6f4ea;
  border-left: 4px solid #092e20;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #145c36;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #092e20 0%, #3fa97b 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #092e2022;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3fa97b 0%, #092e20 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #092e2044;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .django-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .django-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
